44, \"to\": 357}, {\"ngram\": \"commentators\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 374}, {\"ngram\": \"a fault\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 425}, {\"ngram\": \"their supportof ourathletes\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Never once did I hear the wordfailed- that used to curl my toes during the coverage of past Games.\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wordfailed-\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"my toes\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 522}, {\"ngram\": \"the coverage\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 542}, {\"ngram\": \"past Games\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our success was based on many things aligning, but one that is probably underestimated is team culture and the environment the more than 200 athletes operated from.\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our success\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 570}, {\"ngram\": \"many things\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"team culture\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"the environment\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"the more than 200 athletes\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 708}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With any organisation, culture is led from the top.\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any organisation\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 755}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The team's Chef de Mission, Nigel Avery, and his staff should be congratulated for creating a culture that was embraced by each sport's managers, coaches and support systems and, most crucially, the athletes.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 805, \"end\": 816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigel_Avery\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nigel Avery\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigel_Avery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigel_Avery\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The team's Chef de Mission\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 803}, {\"ngram\": \"his staff\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 831}, {\"ngram\": \"a culture\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 878}, {\"ngram\": \"each sport's managers\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 930}, {\"ngram\": \"support systems\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This came through in all television interviews.\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1033, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all television interviews\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A supportive culture breeds success, success breeds pride and this breeds more success.\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"more success\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our nation is being weakened by many issues.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our nation\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1134}, {\"ngram\": \"many issues\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A basic one is a general lack of pride; in ourselves, our family, our environment.\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A basic one\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1180}, {\"ngram\": \"a general lack\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"our environment\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1250}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just as so many of our athletes were helped to excel by their team culture that generated pride and empowered their performances, perhaps we can be inspired by the fact that from more than 200 nations, probably only the Netherlands can match our 2024 Olympics success per capita.\", 